#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/activity_base.html:10
#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/matching/reminder-base.html:7
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "Hi %(recipient_name)s,"
msgstr "Здравей %(recipient_name)s,"

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/activity_manager/activity_approved.html:5
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"Good news, your activity \"%(title)s\" has been approved! It is now live on %(site_name)s for people to contribute.<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Share your activity far and wide to inspire support and attract contributions!\n"
msgstr "\n"
"Добри новини, вашата инициатива \"%(title)s\" е одобрена! Тя е вече активна на %(site_name)s и всеки може да допринася.<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Споделете вашата инициатива навсякъде, за да вдъхновите подкрепа и да привлечете вноски!\n"

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/activity_manager/activity_cancelled.html:6
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "Unfortunately your activity \"%(title)s\" has been cancelled."
msgstr "За съжаление, твоята активност \"%(title)s\" е анулирана."

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/activity_manager/activity_cancelled.html:10
#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/activity_manager/activity_restored.html:14
#: bluebottle/time_based/templates/mails/messages/participant_added_owner.html:10
#: bluebottle/time_based/templates/mails/messages/participant_removed_owner.html:10
#: bluebottle/time_based/templates/mails/messages/participants/manager_participant_removed.html:10
#: bluebottle/time_based/templates/mails/messages/slot_cancelled.html:12
#: bluebottle/time_based/templates/mails/messages/teams/captain_teammember_joined.html:10
#: bluebottle/time_based/templates/mails/messages/teams/captain_teammember_removed.html:10
#: bluebottle/time_based/templates/mails/messages/teams/manager_team_added.html:10
#: bluebottle/time_based/templates/mails/messages/teams/manager_team_removed.html:10
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "If you have any questions, you can contact the platform manager by replying to this email."
msgstr "Ако имаш въпроси, можеш да се свържеш с мениджъра на платформата, като отговориш на този имейл."

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/activity_manager/activity_expired.html:6
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "Unfortunately, nobody applied to your activity \"%(title)s\" before the deadline to apply. That’s why we have cancelled your activity."
msgstr "За съжаление, никой не е подал заявка за вашата дейност \"%(title)s\" преди крайния срок за заявки. Затова анулирахме вашата дейност."

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/activity_manager/activity_expired.html:10
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "Don’t worry, you can always create a new activity and try again."
msgstr "Не се притеснявайте, винаги можете да създадете нова дейност и да опитате отново."

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/activity_manager/activity_expired.html:14
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "Need some tips to make your activity stand out? Reach out to the platform manager by replying to this email."
msgstr "Имаш нужда от съвети, за да направиш активността си да се открои? Свържи се с мениджъра на платформата, като отговориш на този имейл."

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/activity_manager/activity_impact_reminder.html:6
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "We are very curious to know what impact you managed to make with your activity. Please share your results via your activity page."
msgstr "Много ни интересува какъв въздействие успя да направиш с твоята активност. Моля, сподели резултатите си чрез страницата на активността."

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/activity_manager/activity_needs_work.html:5
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"Your activity \"%(title)s\" has been reviewed and needs work. The platform manager\n"
"will be in contact to help you make some changes to your activity.\n"
msgstr "\n"
"Вашата инициатива \"%(title)s\" е прегледана и нуждае се от работа. Платформеният мениджър\n"
"ще се свърже с вас, за да ви помогне да направите някои промени в инициативата си.\n"

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/activity_manager/activity_published.html:5
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"Nice work! Your activity \"%(title)s\" is now live on %(site_name)s for people to contribute.<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Share your activity far and wide to inspire support and attract contributions!\n"
msgstr "\n"
"Чудесна работа! Вашата инициатива \"%(title)s\" вече е активна на %(site_name)s за хората да допринасят.<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Споделете инициативата си навсякъде, за да вдъхновите подкрепа и да привлечете вноски!\n"

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/activity_manager/activity_rejected.html:6
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"        Unfortunately your activity \"%(title)s\" has been rejected.\n"
"        If you have any questions, you can contact the platform manager at %(contact_email)s.\n"
"        "
msgstr "\n"
"        За съжаление, вашата активност \"%(title)s\" е отхвърлена.\n"
"        Ако имате въпроси, можете да се свържете с мениджъра на платформата на %(contact_email)s.\n"
"        "

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/activity_manager/activity_restored.html:6
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "Your activity \"%(title)s\" has been restored."
msgstr "Твоята активност \"%(title)s\" е възстановена."

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/activity_manager/activity_restored.html:10
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "Head over to your activity page to see what you need to do to open up your activity for registrations again."
msgstr "Отиди на страницата на активността си, за да видиш какво трябва да направиш, за да отвориш активността си за нови регистрации отново."

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/activity_manager/activity_submitted.html:5
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"Your activity \"%(title)s\" has been submitted on %(site_name)s.<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<b>What’s next?</b>\n"
"<ul>\n"
"    <li>\n"
"        The platform manager will review your activity.\n"
"    </li>\n"
"    <li>\n"
"        If no changes are needed, it will be approved and made visible on the platform and people can contribute.\n"
"    </li>\n"
"    <li>\n"
"        If any changes are needed, you’ll receive an email with suggested improvements.\n"
"    </li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
msgstr "\n"
"Вашата инициатива \"%(title)s\" е подадена на %(site_name)s.<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<b>Какво следва?</b>\n"
"<ul>\n"
"    <li>\n"
"        Платформеният мениджър ще прегледа вашата инициатива.\n"
"    </li>\n"
"    <li>\n"
"        Ако не са необходими промени, инициативата ще бъде одобрена и ще бъде видима на платформата, за да може хората да допринасят.\n"
"    </li>\n"
"    <li>\n"
"        Ако са необходими промени, ще получите имейл с предложени подобрения.\n"
"    </li>\n"
"</ul>\n"

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/activity_manager/activity_succeeded.html:6
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "You did it! Your activity \"%(title)s\" has succeeded, that calls for a celebration!"
msgstr "Направи го! Твоята активност \"%(title)s\" успя, това е повод за празнуване!"

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/activity_manager/activity_succeeded.html:11
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "Head over to your activity page and enter the impact your activity made, so that everybody can see how effective your activity was."
msgstr "Отиди на страницата на активността си и въведи въздействието, което активността ти е направила, за да може всеки да види колко ефективна е била активността ти."

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/activity_manager/activity_succeeded.html:17
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "And don’t forget to thank your awesome participants for their support."
msgstr "И не забравяйте да благодарите на вашите невероятни участници за тяхната подкрепа."

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/activity_manager/publish_activity_reminder.html:5
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "You have created the activity %(title)s but have not published it yet. This means no one will be able to find your activity and join it."
msgstr "Създаде активността %(title)s, но още нея е публикувал. Това означава, че никой няма да може да намери твоята активност и да се включи."

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/activity_manager/publish_activity_reminder.html:8
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "You can publish your activity from your activity detail page."
msgstr "Можеш да публикуваш активността си от страницата с подробности за активността."

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/activity_manager/terms_of_service.html:7
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"            Thanks for creating a %(activity_type)s for \"%(title)s\". Here are the Terms of Service.\n"
"        "
msgstr "\n"
"            Благодаря, че създадохте %(activity_type)s за \"%(title)s\". Ето Общите условия.\n"
"        "

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/matching/matching_activities.html:7
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"            There are tons of cool activities on %(site_name)s that are making a positive impact.\n\n"
"            We have selected %(count)s activities that match with your profile. Join us!\n"
"        "
msgstr "\n"
"            Има много страхотни активности на %(site_name)s, които правят положително въздействие.\n\n"
"            Избрахме %(count)s активности, които отговарят на вашия профил. Присъединете се към нас!\n"
"        "

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/matching/matching_activities.html:17
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "Complete your profile"
msgstr "Завършете профила си"

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/matching/matching_activities.html:19
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid ", so that we can select even more relevant activities for you."
msgstr ", за да можем да изберем още по-релевантни активности за вас."

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/matching/matching_activities.html:44
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "Online / Remote"
msgstr "Онлайн / Дистанционно"

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/matching/matching_activities.html:73
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "No specific skill needed"
msgstr "Не се изисква специфичен умение"

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/matching/matching_activities.html:96
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "Don't want to receive this monthly update anymore? Unsubscribe"
msgstr "Не искате да получавате повече този месечен отчет? Отпишете се"

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/matching/matching_activities.html:97
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "via your profile page."
msgstr "чрез страницата на профила си."

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/matching/reminder-base.html:18
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"      Go to <a href=\"%(profile_url)s\">your profile</a> to opt-out.\n"
"    "
msgstr "\n"
"      Отидете на <a href=\"%(profile_url)s\">вашия профил</a>, за да се отпишете.\n"
"    "

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/matching/reminder-q1.html:6
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"    Ready to make an impact from day one? On %(site_name)s you’ll find many activities waiting for you.\n"
"    "
msgstr "\n"
"    Готови ли сте да направите въздействие от първия ден? На %(site_name)s ще намерите много дейности, които ви чакат.\n"
"    "

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/matching/reminder-q1.html:11
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"    Take a look and you might discover your next passion project!\n"
"    "
msgstr "\n"
"    Погледнете и може да откриете следващия си страстен проект!\n"
"    "

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/matching/reminder-q1.html:21
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"    Even a small step can lead to big impact. Let’s make it happen!\n"
"    "
msgstr "\n"
"    Дори и малка стъпка може да доведе до голямо въздействие. Нека го направим!"

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/matching/reminder-q2.html:6
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"    We know that getting started can sometimes be the hardest part. That’s why we’ve made it simple to find activities that match your interests and time.\n"
"    "
msgstr "\n"
"    Знаем, че понякога започването може да бъде най-трудната част. Затова направихме лесно да намерите дейности, които съответстват на вашите интереси и време.\n"
"    "

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/matching/reminder-q2.html:11
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"    Ready to explore %(site_name)s? Just click below to find activities that fit your schedule.\n"
"    "
msgstr "\n"
"    Готови ли сте да изследвате %(site_name)s? Просто кликнете долу, за да намерите дейности, които ви пасват."

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/matching/reminder-q2.html:20
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"    Remember, even small actions can lead to big impact. We’re here to support you every step of the way.\n"
"    "
msgstr "\n"
"    Не забравяйте, дори малките действия могат да доведат до голямо въздействие. Ние сме тук, за да ви подкрепим на всяка крачка от пътя.\n"
"    "

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/matching/reminder-q3.html:6
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"    We’re halfway through the year and there’s still lots of opportunity to make impact. Whether you’ve got a few minutes or a few hours, your efforts can make a real difference.\n"
"    "
msgstr "\n"
"    Половината от годината е изминала и все още има много възможности да направите въздействие. Независимо дали имате няколко минути или няколко часа, вашите усилия могат да направят реална разлика.\n"
"    "

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/matching/reminder-q3.html:11
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"    Take a moment to explore the activities waiting for you.\n"
"    "
msgstr "\n"
"    Отделете момент, за да разгледате дейностите, които ви чакат.\n"
"    "

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/matching/reminder-q3.html:21
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"    Every action counts. Let's see what we can accomplish together in the coming months.\n"
"    "
msgstr "\n"
"    Всяко действие е важно. Нека видим какво можем да постигнем заедно през идните месеци.\n"
"    "

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/matching/reminder-q4.html:6
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"    As we approach the final months of the year, there’s still time to make impact. Many causes would benefit from your time and skills.\n"
"    "
msgstr "\n"
"    Докато приближаваме към последните месеци на годината, все още има време да направите въздействие. Много каузи биха се възползвали от вашето време и умения.\n"
"    "

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/matching/reminder-q4.html:11
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"    Ready to end the year on a high note?\n"
"    "
msgstr "\n"
"    Готови ли сте да завършите годината с вълнение?\n"
"    "

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/matching/reminder-q4.html:21
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"    Your involvement matters. Let's work together to close out the year with meaningful impact.\n"
"    "
msgstr "\n"
"    Вашето участие е важно. Нека работим заедно, за да завършим годината с значимо въздействие.\n"
"    "

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/participant/inactive_participant_added.html:6
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"<p>You have been added to an activity on %(site_name)s</p>\n"
msgstr "\n"
"<p>Добавени сте в активност в %(site_name)s</p>\n"

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/participant/inactive_participant_added.html:10
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"<p>View the activity to learn more about what’s planned and what to expect. We'll ask you to activate your account to stay updated which will make it easier to join future activities.</p>\n"
msgstr "\n"
"<p>Прегледайте дейността, за да научите повече за планираното и какво да очаквате. Ще ви помолим да активирате вашия акаунт, за да останете актуални, което ще улесни присъединяването към бъдещи дейности.</p>\n"

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/participant/inactive_participant_added.html:19
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"            View activity \n"
"        "
msgstr "\n"
"            Прегледайте активността \n"
"        "

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/participant/participant_withdrew_confirmation.html:4
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"<p>You have withdrawn from an activity on <b>%(site_name)s</b></p>\n\n"
"<p>\n"
"    <b>%(title)s</b>\n"
"</p>\n"
msgstr "\n"
"<p>Отказа се от активност на <b>%(site_name)s</b></p>\n\n"
"<p>\n"
"    <b>%(title)s</b>\n"
"</p>\n"

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/reviewer/activity_published.html:5
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"The activity \"%(title)s\" has been successfully published\n"
"and is now live on %(site_name)s for people to contribute to.\n"
msgstr "\n"
"Инициативата \"%(title)s\" е успешно публикувана\n"
"и вече е активна на %(site_name)s, за да могат хората да допринасят.\n"

#: bluebottle/activities/templates/mails/messages/reviewer/activity_submitted.html:5
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"The activity \"%(title)s\" has been submitted by %(initiator_name)s.<br>\n"
"Please take a moment to review this activity and decide if it's right for your platform.<br>\n"
"%(initiator_name)s will be waiting for your review, so please respond promptly.<br>\n"
msgstr "\n"
"Инициативата \"%(title)s\" е подадена от %(initiator_name)s.<br>\n"
"Моля, отделете миг, за да прегледате инициативата и да кажете дали е подходяща за вашата платформа.<br>\n"
"%(initiator_name)s ще очаква прегледа ви, така че моля отговорете бързо.<br>\n"

