#: bluebottle/time_based/templates/mails/messages/registrations/schedule/user_joined.html:6
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"          You joined an activity on <b>%(site_name)s!</b>\n"
"        "
msgstr "\n"
"          Включихте се в активността на <b>%(site_name)s!</b>\n"
"        "

#: bluebottle/time_based/templates/mails/messages/registrations/team_accepted.html:5
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"        <p>Good news, your team has been accepted for the activity \"%(title)s\"!</p>\n"
"        <p>If your team is unable to participate, please withdraw via the activity page so that others can take your place.</p>\n"
"    "
msgstr "\n"
"        <p>Добри новини, екипът ви е приет за активността \"%(title)s\"!</p>\n"
"        <p>Ако вашият екип не може да участва, моля, оттеглете се през страницата на активността, за да могат другите да заемат вашето място.</p>\n"
"    "

#: bluebottle/time_based/templates/mails/messages/registrations/team_rejected.html:4
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"<p>Unfortunately, your team has not been selected for the activity ‘%(title)s’.</p>\n\n"
"<p>Don’t worry, there are more activities out there that need your help. Head over to the activity overview page to see if there is something for you.</p>\n"
msgstr "\n"
"<p>За съжаление, вашият екип не е избран за дейността ‘%(title)s’.</p>\n\n"
"<p>Не се притеснявайте, има много дейности, които се нуждаят от вашата помощ. Отидете на страницата с преглед на дейности, за да видите дали има нещо за вас.</p>\n"

#: bluebottle/time_based/templates/mails/messages/registrations/user_accepted.html:6
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"            <p>Good news, you have been accepted for the activity \"%(title)s\"!</p>\n"
"        "
msgstr "\n"
"            <p>Добри новини, вие сте приети за активността \"%(title)s\"!</p>\n"
"        "

#: bluebottle/time_based/templates/mails/messages/registrations/user_removed.html:4
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"<p>Unfortunately, you have been removed from the activity ‘%(title)s’.</p>\n\n"
"<p>\n"
"    Don’t worry, there are more activities out there that need your help. Head\n"
"    over to the activity overview page to see if there is something for you.\n"
"</p>\n"
msgstr "\n"
"<p>За съжаление, вие сте премахнати от дейността ‘%(title)s’.</p>\n\n"
"<p>\n"
"    Не се притеснявайте, има много дейности, които се нуждаят от вашата помощ. Отидете на страницата с преглед на дейности, за да видите дали има нещо за вас.\n"
"</p>\n"

#: bluebottle/time_based/templates/mails/messages/registrations/user_restarted.html:5
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"      <p>You have restarted your contribution to \"%(title)s\".</p>\n"
"      <p>Good to have you on board again! You are expected to contribute approximately <b>%(duration)s hours every %(period)s</b>.</p>\n"
"    "
msgstr "\n"
"      <p>Вие сте възстановили вашето участие в \"%(title)s\".</p>\n"
"      <p>Добре е отново да ви имаме на борда! Очаква се да допринасяте приблизително <b>%(duration)s часа всеки %(period)s</b>.</p>\n"
"    "

#: bluebottle/time_based/templates/mails/messages/registrations/user_stopped.html:5
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"        <p>You have stopped your contributions to \"%(title)s\".</p>\n"
"        <p>Thanks for taking part in our activity, your contributions have been counted.</p>\n"
"        <p>You can always restart your contributions anytime.</p>\n"
"    "
msgstr "\n"
"        <p>Спряхте вашето участие в \"%(title)s\".</p>\n"
"        <p>Благодарим, че взехте участие в нашата активност, вашите участия са били отчетени.</p>\n"
"        <p>Винаги можете да възобновите вашето участие по всяко време.</p>\n"
"    "

#: bluebottle/time_based/templates/mails/messages/reminder_slot.html:5
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"The activity will take place tomorrow!\n"
msgstr "\n"
"Активността ще се проведе утре!\n"

#: bluebottle/time_based/templates/mails/messages/reminder_team_slot.html:5
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"The team activity is just a few days away!\n"
msgstr "\n"
"Екипната активност е само след няколко дни!\n"

#: bluebottle/time_based/templates/mails/messages/reminder_team_slot.html:20
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"Please view your team from the activity page.\n"
msgstr "\n"
"Моля, вижте екипа си от страницата на активността.\n"

#: bluebottle/time_based/templates/mails/messages/reviewer/activity_registered.html:5
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
