"<p>You have been added to team \"%(team_name)s\" for the activity \"%(title)s\".</p>\n\n"
"<p>Head over to the activity page for more information.</p>\n\n"
msgstr "\n"
"<p>Добавени сте в екипа \"%(team_name)s\" за активността \"%(title)s\".</p>\n\n"
"<p>Посетете страницата на активността за повече информация.</p>\n\n"

#: bluebottle/time_based/templates/mails/messages/team_participant_applied.html:6
